These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different games are played: chess, bridge, canasta, backgammon, billiard, whist, scrabble
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indonesian, italian, nigerian, spanish, thai
 1. the thai is the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the brazilian is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
 3. the brazilian is not to the left of the french##8
 4. the french is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 5. the person playing chess is not to the left of the spanish##8
 6. the person playing chess is not the french##6
 7. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 9. the nigerian is somewhere between the thai and the french##7
10. the french is the person playing whist##1
11. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
12. the spanish is on the right of the thai##1
13. the brazilian is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
14. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the nigerian and the brazilian##7
15. the person playing whist is on the left of the brazilian##1
16. the spanish is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
17. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
18. the person playing scrabble is the indonesian##1
19. the nigerian is on the left or right of the thai##3
20. the person playing backgammon is not the spanish##6
21. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
22. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Game           | whist | canasta | scrabble | bridge  | billiard  | backgammon | chess    |
| Nationality   | french   | brazilian   | indonesian   | italian | nigerian | thai        | spanish |

