.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, camping, dancing, drawing, filmmaking, photography, puzzles
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, skiing, ice-hockey, snowboarding, handball, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 4. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
14. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
15. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
