 6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is golf##2
13. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the person drinking juice##6
14. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

